{"tid":1811403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【ALERT】藍絲民意即將逆博","createTime":"2020-01-04T16:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T16:13:36.000Z","uid":267622,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48f1fce94c5fc9ba8d10f7a59850639c95f9f88e","tid":1811403,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係時候搞個「全城抗疫 港中分隔」大遊行</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾政權已經將民意核彈送咗畀我哋</span></strong><br />\n唔用好個核彈揼扁佢真係唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記唔記得03年之後董建華係點落台？<br />\n23條？係，但仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沙士</span></strong></span></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n武漢單嘢咁大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論你係藍定黃都會出事<br />\n<br />\n一於食住呢單嘢<br />\n利用港豬自保嘅心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要求政權做好<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港中分隔</span></strong><br />\n最好<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">騎劫埋啲淺藍</span></strong>一齊去行，咁就真正做到we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府打壓我哋嘅後果係咩？<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">係將啲淺藍嘅民意都送哂畀我哋</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7328da1493007b22598f0a43ea4500ccc5e3e892","tid":1811403,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2a74603419d7ad0cf2fd5473a694eedef9ffc95","tid":1811403,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"36ad6ba5f3ce50a4a95564aa038196a7cdffd076","tid":1811403,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57a429949787f306d788a04cf1ce5a1b516540da","tid":1811403,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"